abstract: The press was not allowed into an Oval Office session between President Trump and Sergey V. Lavrov. Then the official Russian news agency published pictures of the event.
snippet: The press was not allowed into an Oval Office session between President Trump and Sergey V. Lavrov. Then the official Russian news agency published pictures of the event.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — What is it about Sergey V. Lavrov that always makes high-ranking American officials look hapless?

abstract: The Republicans working on a bill to replace much of the Affordable Care Act do not include a woman or the moderates who could determine its fate.
snippet: The Republicans working on a bill to replace much of the Affordable Care Act do not include a woman or the moderates who could determine its fate.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The top Republican in the Senate, Mitch McConnell of Kentucky, has a reputation as a shrewd tactician and a wily strategist — far more than his younger counterpart in the House, Speaker Paul D. Ryan.

headline_main: California Today: Down to the Wire in Hollywood

abstract: In a largely leaderless party, two distinct groups are emerging, defined mostly by age and national stature.
snippet: In a largely leaderless party, two distinct groups are emerging, defined mostly by age and national stature.
lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. — A vast array of Democratic leaders, divided by generations but uniformly emboldened by President Trump’s perceived vulnerability, have begun taking palpable steps toward seeking the White House in an election that is still three and a half years away.
